  <CalDefinition Description="TTY Lockout to be overridden during an Emergency Call. Do not lockout TTY mode when making or receiving an Emergency Call. This only applies to OnStar emergency calls and is not applicable to OnStar personal calls or Bluetooth personal/emergency behavior.  " Name="TtyEmergencyCallDriverWorkload" References="GIS503 5.5.1.1*MY17 Driver Workload Restriction Items" Usage="LOW,MID,HIGH,GEM,GLOBALA,GLOBALB,ENTRY_VCU,VCU">
